    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.308889553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日のシメは……ででん！　カラオケでしたー！\n最後にみんなで盛り上がっちゃおー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To end this birthday celebration… ta-da! Karaoke~!\nLet’s all have fun together at the end~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村調べやと高校生の誕生日の大半は\nここで過ごすみたいやで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "According to my research‚ most high school birthday\ncelebrations end here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6627634354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0511114438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのね。確かにいつもと違った空間で歌うのも\n気持ちが良さそうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It does seem like it would feel good to\nsing in a place that’s different from usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3177781105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3511114438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "それに……最近のカラオケってこんなに広いのね\n設備もマイクスタンドにスクリーンまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… karaoke places these days are so spacious.\nThe facilities‚ too‚ from mic stands to screens…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5511114438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6844447772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "こんなん最近は普通やで\nこれはたまには瑠依ちゃんを街に連れ出さなあかんな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is normal these days.\nWe should take Rui out on the town more often~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも、ドリンクバー取りに行こうよ！\nちらっと見たけど、沢山種類があるみたいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ you two‚ want to go to the drink bar?\nI took a peek‚ and it looks like they have a lot of options.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5951798539,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4854.182169700003,
          "startTime": 48.4493620236
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2160302162
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2160302162
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3493635495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　少し混んでるわね。あっ、高校生の\nカップル……デートかしら。あっ！　手を繋いでる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my? It’s a bit crowded. Ah‚ a high school\ncouple… are they on a date? Ah! They're holding hands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8935549669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.3493620236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうよね、普通の、こっ高校生はああやって\n男女で遊んでいるのよねっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that’s right… normal h-high schoolers…\nhang out like that…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3493635495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7160286903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、今日はとことん普通の高校生とのギャップを\n感じる日やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ today’s the day you get to fully experience the difference\nbetween you and a normal high schooler.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん！　いつもは寝てる時もアイドルのこと\nトリエルのことに全力だもんね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes! You’re always thinking about being an idol‚\nabout TRINITYAiLE‚ even when you’re sleeping!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1095125004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7948271114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、また二人してからかってるわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you two are teasing me again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7948271114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.3948271114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、冗談やんか。でも、瑠依ちゃんもああいうのに\n憧れるん？　カラオケで男の子と一緒に遊んだり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ I was just kidding. But‚ do Rui-chan long for that kind of thing‚ too?\nHanging out with a boy at karaoke…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.5330586749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　そ、そんなんじゃないわ\nそもそも仲がいい男の子なんていないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what?! N-no way!\nI don’t even have any close male friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5663935342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9330586749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、瑠依ちゃんがアイドル以外を選ぶなんて\n考えられないよ。だって時間が空けばレッスンだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I can’t imagine Rui-chan choosing anything other than being an idol.\nAfter all‚ whenever you have free time‚ you’re practicing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5997268675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8663920083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ。瑠依ちゃんは練習の鬼やから\nデートもレッスンスタジオかもなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Rui-chan always practices a lot‚\nso maybe your dates would be at the lesson room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.677979628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "デートは普通に公園とか行くわよ！　……でも\n確かに今はアイドル以外のことを考えられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dates are usually at parks or something! …But\nit’s true that right now‚ I can't think of anything other than idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.3446478205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7779781021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "それでこそ瑠依ちゃんだよ！\nじゃあドリンクバーは後にしよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s our Rui-chan for you!\nLet’s go to the drink bar later then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4446462946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.6113190648
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.6113190648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "フードのメニューも充実してるみたいやで\nなんか注文してみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The food menu looks great‚ too.\nWant to order something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9649812318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.2968504266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "メニューを見せてもらえるかしら\nきゃっ！　停電！？　優、すみれ、大丈夫……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I see the menu?\nKyaa! A blackout?! Yu‚ Sumire‚ are you okay…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8645968117,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5502.068329099984,
          "startTime": 149.3666651408
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9435.401662399983,
          "startTime": 153.2999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　私は大丈夫！\n瑠依ちゃん、危ないから動かないでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! I’m okay!\nRui-chan‚ don’t move‚ it’s dangerous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.696845849,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4503.1526251000005,
          "startTime": 156.1999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.5968504266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
